OL,3,CExcitement builds as crowds gather for
OL,4,Cinstallation of Archbishop of
OL,5,CCanterbury
OL,7,FChristians gathered outside Canterbury
OL,8,FCathedral have expressed their
OL,9,Fexcitement ahead of Dame Sarah
OL,10,FMullally's installation as the first
OL,11,Ffemale Archbishop of Canterbury.
OL,13,FA crowd of people were outside the
OL,14,Fcathedral on Wednesday ahead of the
OL,15,Fservice to mark the symbolic start of
OL,16,FDame Sarah's ministry as the first
OL,17,Fwoman to hold the Church's highest
OL,18,Foffice in its 1,400 year history.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
