CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774461963
OL,3,CExcitement builds as crowds gather for
OL,4,Cinstallation of Archbishop of
OL,5,CCanterbury
OL,7,FNiles Schilder, 23, from Canterbury,
OL,8,FKent, said he was feeling "fantastic"
OL,9,Fbefore the service.
OL,11,F"The atmosphere in Canterbury is
OL,12,Falways brilliant, but today especially
OL,13,Fthere's such anticipation, such
OL,14,Fexcitement," he told the Press
OL,15,FAssociation.
OL,26,@pD@[OUpD@eO]vD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
