PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774461963
OL,3,CExcitement builds as crowds gather for
OL,4,Cinstallation of Archbishop of
OL,5,CCanterbury
OL,7,F"I'm determined to see it out and get
OL,8,Fto the end and see this brilliant
OL,9,Fmoment in history."Mr Schilder, who
OL,10,Fhad been waiting outside the cathedral
OL,11,Fsince 10am, said Dame Sarah was an
OL,12,F"absolutely fantastic" choice for
OL,13,FArchbishop."
OL,15,FAlso in the crowd was Julie, who had
OL,16,Fbeen outside the cathedral since 7am.
OL,18,F"It's just such a fantastic moment in
OL,19,Fhistory that I couldn't not be here.
OL,20,FAnd I've come down from York
OL,21,Fespecially for it," she said.
OL,26,@qD@SO]tD@AOUtD@VO]zD@AOU}D@SO]
