PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774461963
OL,3,CExcitement builds as crowds gather for
OL,4,Cinstallation of Archbishop of
OL,5,CCanterbury
OL,7,FAsked what she thought of Dame Sarah,
OL,8,FJulie said: "She's ace."
OL,10,FSpeaking to PA outside the cathedral,
OL,11,FRhiannon King, the Bishop of
OL,12,FSouthampton, said she was "super,
OL,13,Fsuper excited".
OL,15,F"I never thought this day would
OL,16,Fhappen. I feel the whole place, the
OL,17,Fwhole of Canterbury, let alone the
OL,18,FCathedral, is full of hope and joy,"
OL,19,Fshe said.
OL,26,@pD@MOUpD@XO]tD@[OUuD@NO]zD@dO]
