PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774461963
OL,3,CExcitement builds as crowds gather for
OL,4,Cinstallation of Archbishop of
OL,5,CCanterbury
OL,7,FBishop King, who was with Dame Sarah
OL,8,Fahead of the service, said the
OL,9,FArchbishop was "full of hope".
OL,11,FAsked whether Dame Sarah would tackle
OL,12,Fthe challenges facing the Church,
OL,13,FBishop King said: "I think she will
OL,14,Fhave the best possible shot. Lots of
OL,15,Fthings to address, but she will do a
OL,16,Fgreat job."
OL,18,FA queue of hundreds of people had
OL,19,Fformed outside the cathedral ahead of
OL,20,Fthe ceremony later on Wednesday.
OL,26,@qD@POUqD@]O]uD@SOUxD@KO]
